name: ✨ release ✨
description:
For this ritual, I ask you to visualize yourself placing all of your insecurities, fears, self-judgements, old ties to others and anything else you would like to release, into a cleansing blue fire.

I hope my final offering aids you in releasing all that no longer serves you 💙

My final offering for this years #WitchingHourOnHEN ♏🖤
